overview: Claudio Castagnoli wants to teach a lesson to all The Kings of Wrestling, and starts with Chuck Taylor! Tim Donst gets a rematch against Eddie Kingston. Mitch Ryder still hates luchadores, and attacks Lince Dorado! F.I.S.T. defends los Campeonatos de Parejas against Incoherence in the main event.
title: Chikara: Bruised
